name: primetime_tv
description:
I don't have to tell you things are bad. Everybody knows things are bad.

- Howard Beale

This piece was hand-drawn (with mouse and stylus) and animated using Aseprite. Its seamless loop consists 960 frames. Each frame lasts 42 milliseconds. The colors are derived from the PICO-8 palette and opacity blending. 576x576. 91.5MB.
